納姆","York, Yorkshire, England":"英國越可爾約克","Banham, Norfolk, England":"英國諾福爾可班納姆","England":"英國","lifeSummary":"當Richard Micklewood de Clare Earl of Pembrooke於1505年出生在英國諾福爾可班納姆時，他的父親Gilbert De Clare25歲，母親Elizabeth Isabel de Beaumont25歲。他於1525年與Lady Elizabeth Anne Bishop de Bourgogne在英國英格蘭諾福爾可班納姆結婚。他們至少是3個女兒的父母。他去世於1559年2月20日在他的家鄉享年54歲，埋葬在英國諾福爾可班納姆。"},"zh-hans":{"1505– 20 February 1559":"1505年–1559年2月20日","1505–1559":"1505年–1559年","1502–1559":"1502年–1559年","1529–1559":"1529年–1559年","1531–1593":"1531年–1593年","1480–1550":"1480年–1550年","1480–1505":"1480年–1505年","1550":"1550年","Aft. 1505":"1505年之后","1593":"1593年","1480":"1480年","1525":"1525年"," 20 February 1559":"1559年2月20日","1558":"1558年","1502":"1502年","1531":"1531年","about 1559":"大约1559年","1529":"1529年","20 February 1559":"1559年2月20日","1505":"1505年","1549":"1549年","1559":"1559年","Saint Mary the Virgin Church, Banham, Norfolk, England":"英国諾福爾可班納姆","York, Yorkshire, England":"英国越可爾約克","Banham, Norfolk, England":"英国諾福爾可班納姆","England":"英国","lifeSummary":"当Richard Micklewood de Clare Earl of Pembrooke于1505年出生在英国諾福爾可班納姆时，他的父亲Gilbert De Clare25岁，母亲Elizabeth Isabel de Beaumont25岁。他于1525年与Lady Elizabeth Anne Bishop de Bourgogne在英国英格兰諾福爾可班納姆结婚。他们至少是3个女儿的父母。他去世于1559年2月20日在他的家乡享年54岁，埋葬在英国諾福爾可班納姆。"},"hr":{"1505– 20 February 1559":"1505.–20. veljače 1559.","1505–1559":"1505.–1559","1502–1559":"1502–1559","1529–1559":"1529.–1559","1531–1593":"1531.–1593","1480–1550":"1480–1550.","1480–1505":"1480–1505.","1550":"1550.","Aft. 1505":"nakon 1505.","1593":"1593","1480":"1480","1525":"1525."," 20 February 1559":"20. veljače 1559.","1558":"1558","1502":"1502","1531":"1531.","about 1559":"oko 1559.","1529":"1529.","20 February 1559":"20. veljače 1559.","1505":"1505.","1549":"1549","1559":"1559","Saint Mary the Virgin Church, Banham, Norfolk, England":"Banham, Norfolk, England","York, Yorkshire, England":"York, Yorkshire, England","Banham, Norfolk, England":"Banham, Norfolk, England","England":"England"},"cs":{"1505– 20 February 1559":"1505–20